description:
1）协助投资经理做好权益市场和债券市场的投资研究，协助制定股票、债券的投资计划、投资策略。

Assist investment managers in the investment research of equity market and bond market, including formulating investment plans and investment strategies for stocks and bonds.

2）进行行业和公司的基本面研究，挖掘投资机会；

Follow up, research and analyze the fundamentals of industries and companies, and explore investment opportunities;

3）协助投资经理跟踪持仓个股，并提出投资建议；

Help investment managers keep track of individual stocks held and make investment recommendations independently;

4）保持与市场中其他机构投资者、上市公司、研究员的紧密联系和沟通；

Maintain close contact and communication with other institutional investors, listed companies, and researchers in the market;

5）完成部门和公司交办的其他事项。

Organize the implementation and completion of other matters assigned by the department and the company.

Responsibilities:

Maintain and develop trustful relationship with existing and potential clients;
Handle daily phone/online customer enquiries and complaints;
Provide back-end support to the sales team on client's enquiries;
Undate and maintain customer information on database;
Participate in warm call, ad-hoc projects as assigned.

 Requirement & Qualification:

Form 5 or above (Passed in Chinese and Mathematics/ English and Mathematics) is a must;
One year of telesales experience, fresh graduates are also welcomed ;
Hardworking, responsible and good communication skills;
Good customer services and telephone manners;
Good command of spoken and written English and Chinese including Putonghua.

 We Offer:

Competitive remuneration package
5 Days Work & Bank Holidays
Attendance Bonus
Meal Allowance
Discretionary Bonus
Medical Insurance
On the Job Training

We provide attractive remuneration package and fringe benefits for the right candidate.

Interested parties please send detailed resume with current and expected salaries to Human Resources Department by clicking "Apply Now" or fax to: 2530 2218.

All information collected will be used for recruitment purpose only, only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Welcome to visit our website: http://www.bsgroup.com.hk/ for more information.

Responsibilities:

To assist drafting the Group’s integrated risk management report;
To assist drafting risk management policies;
To assist drafting the Group’s risk management strategies and annual work plan;
To coordinate the consolidation of risk management information from various risk management units;
To coordinate implementing risk management projects;
To keep track of changes in macro economies, regulatory requirements and business development, analyze its impact on risk management, and propose risk management measures accordingly;
To assist assessing effectiveness of single type risk management and identifying management loopholes;
To assist establishing new types of risks, crossover risks, risks infection, risks aggregation management mechanism; coordinating crossover risks management; strengthening risks infection monitoring.

Requirements:

Qualifications of degree or above, major in Economics, Finance, Accounting, Business & Administration or relevant professions;
Working experience of 5 years or above in bank with at least 2 years in risk management, such as credit risk, market risk, interest risk;
Excellent analytical, problem solving, communication and language skills;
Familiar with MS Office software, such as MS Word, Excel and PowerPoint;
Excellent Chinese and English.

We offer competitive remuneration package and comprehensive fringe benefits including medical and life insurance, and different types of allowances to the right candidate. Interested parties, please submit your application online. For details, please visit our website http://www.bochk.com

[via APPLY NOW]  

Data collected would be used for recruitment purposes only. It might also be disclosed to our subsidiaries or Associated Companies to process the information for appointment. Applicants who do not hear from us within 8 weeks may consider their application unsuccessful and their data will be destroyed within 12 months of receipt.
